ActNunavut Act
PrecisAppointment of REBEKAH UQI WILLIAMS of Iqaluit, Nunavut, to be Deputy Commissioner of Nunavut to execute the office and functions of the Commissioner during the absence or illness or other inability of the latter or when the office of Commissioner is vacant, for a term of three years, effective upon taking and subscribing the oath of office and the oath of allegiance prescribed under section 9 of the Nunavut Act.
